        <mxCell id="c2_0" parent="1" vertex="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#ffe6cc;strokeColor=#d79b00;fontSize=11;arcSize=8;" value="&lt;b&gt;Book Authoring &amp; Generation&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Book-scoped 6-dim topics (ADR-009)&lt;br&gt;• Free-text TOC → structure&lt;br&gt;• Lesson / explanation / quiz gen&lt;br&gt;• Regenerate-with-reason · topic-tree editor&lt;br&gt;• Collaborative draft sharing + comments">
