        <mxCell id="foot" parent="1" vertex="1" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=middle;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontColor=#666666;" value="Solid • = live in code; grey ◦ = designed / built-but-off / partial (marker in text: (planned)=spec only, (built, off)/(gated)=code-complete but disabled, (partial)=partly shipped). Dashed card = whole group not yet live. All three apps share the wegofwd-llm seam (and wegofwd-secure for key handling); pramana + kathai-chithiram also share wegofwd-video (ADR-026); Mentible adds a shared wegofwd-help package (planned) — see shared_library.drawio. Verified against each repo README / docs / ADRs / source, 2026-07-07.">
